RÉCOR — Licensing notice
========================

The default licensing posture for this repository is Restricted.

The source code in this repository is the property of the RÉCOR Consortium
(Ministry of Finance, Ministry of Justice, and the ten consortium member
institutions of the Republic of Cameroon).

Distribution outside the consortium is governed by the consortium's documented
contribution and distribution processes (CONTRIBUTING.md, Architecture V1 P4
OPSEC).

Specific components are released under the Apache License, Version 2.0
(Apache-2.0) as committed in Architecture V3 P10 (Open-source commitments).
These components are explicitly marked in their package metadata, and the full
Apache-2.0 text accompanies each released artefact.

Components currently in scope for open release under Apache-2.0 include:

  - Platform data-model schemas
  - The BODS export adapter
  - The verification engine's pattern-detection signature definitions
    (without trained classifier weights)
  - Cryptographic substrate adapters
  - Consumer integration adapters in genericised form
  - User-facing application frontends

Components NOT released:

  - Trained pattern-detection classifier weights
  - Deployment configurations and secrets
  - Internal operational documentation
  - Any code whose disclosure would materially aid adversarial circumvention
    of the verification engine

For licensing questions, contact legal@recor.cm.
